    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Please keep the github issues for problems you face when either installing or running the software. For other questions you can refer to our [discord](https://discord.gg/nthXNEv) or [StackExchange](https://ethereum.stackexchange.com).\r\n\r\nYou can find installation instructions here: https://geth.ethereum.org/docs/install-and-build/installing-geth. You won't need a full node, simply run the default sync option (snap). Snap sync should be done in a few hours. Then either use the console to get the balances or if you want something programmable enable the `--http` and `--http.api eth` then you can send requests to `localhost:8545`.",
